products.description:
Everything is super with the all-new ZOTAC GAMING GeForce RTX Series SUPER graphics cards. Based on the NVIDIA Turing architecture, it's packed with more Cores and ultra-fast GDDR6 memory. Integrated with more smart and optimized technologies, get ready to GET FAST and GAME STRONG.

FEATURES
• IceStorm 2.0 Cooling
• Super Compact
• Wraparound Metal Backplate
• White LED Lighting
• Real-time Ray Tracing and DLSS support
• 4K, VR and HDR Ready
• NVIDIA Ansel
• NVIDIA G-SYNC compatible
• NVLinkTM (SLI-ready)

SPECIFICATIONS
• NVIDIA GeForce RTX 2070 SUPER GPU
• 2560 CUDA cores
• 8GB GDDR6 memory
• 256-bit memory bus
• Engine boost clock: 1770 MHz
• Memory clock: 14.0 Gbps
• PCI Express 3.0

CONNECTIONS
• 3 x DisplayPort 1.4 (up to 7680x4320@60Hz)
• HDMI 2.0b (up to 3840x2160@60Hz)
• Quad simultaneous display capable

POWER REQUIREMENTS
• 650-watt power supply recommended
• 215-watt max power consumption

SOFTWARE COMPATIBILITY
• Game Ready Drivers
• Microsoft DirectX 12 API, Vulkan API
• OpenGL 4.5
• Microsoft Windows 10/7 64-bit, Linux 64-bit

INSIDE THE BOX
• ZOTAC GAMING GeForce RTX 2070 SUPER MINI
• Dual 6-pin to 8-pin cable
• Dual 4-pin to 6-pin cable
• User Manual

DIMENSIONS
• Length: 209.6mm (8.25in)
• Height: 126.1mm (4.96in)
• Width: Dual slot (41mm) (1.61in)
• Box
• Height: 283mm (11.1in)
• Width: 218mm (8.6in)
• Depth: 83mm (3.3in).
